tafsir[2]{c,v,t}:
  46,23,"He said: \"The Knowledge (of when it will come) is only with Allah: I proclaim to you the mission on which I have been sent: But I see that ye are a people in ignorance!\".."
  46,25,"\"Everything will it destroy by the command of its Lord!\" Then by the morning they - nothing was to be seen but (the ruins of) their houses! thus do We recompense those given to sin!"